{"title_page": "Franck Khalfoun", "text_new": "{{Infobox person\n|name=Franck Khalfoun\n|image=Franck Khalfoun.jpg\n|image_size=200px\n|caption=Khalfoun at the [[2012 Cannes Film Festival]]\n|birth_name=Franck Ange Khalfoun\n|birth_date={{birth date and age|df=y|1968|3|9}}\n|birth_place=[[Paris]], [[France]]\n|occupation=[[Film director]], [[screenwriter]]\n|years_active=1992\u2013present\n}}\n\n'''Franck Ange Khalfoun''' (born 9 March 1968 in [[Paris]], [[\u00cele-de-France]], France) is a French film director and screenwriter, known for directing ''[[P2 (film)|P2]]'', ''[[Wrong Turn at Tahoe]]'', ''[[Maniac (2012 film)|Maniac]]'',<ref>{{Cite web |work=[[The New York Times]] |title=The Timid Guy With the Slasher Knife |first=Nicolas |last=Rapold |date=June 20, 2013 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/21/movies/maniac-goes-inside-a-killer-played-by-elijah-wood.html?_r=0}}</ref> and the [[Amityville (film series)|''Amityville'' franchise]] entry ''[[Amityville: The Awakening]]''.<ref>{{Cite web |work=[[Dread Central]] |title=Amityville: The Awakening Release Update |first=Steve |last=Barton |date=February 25, 2015 |url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/91104/amityville-awakening-release-update/}}</ref> His upcoming films include the horror film ''[[Prey (2019 American film)|Prey]]''<ref>{{Cite web |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |title=Hyde Park-Image Nation & Blumhouse Partner For \u2018Prey\u2019 |first=Anthony |last=D'Allessandro |date=June 6, 2016 |url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/prey-logan-miller-blumhouse-hyde-park-1201769872/}}</ref> and the action-thriller film ''Entry Level''.<ref>{{Cite web |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |title=\u2018Entry Level\u2019 Staffs Up With Director Franck Khalfoun, \u2018Final Destination\u2019 Duo |first=Erik |last=Pederson |date=April 30, 2015 |url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/entry-level-franck-khalfoun-final-destination-producers-1201418258/}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n===Feature films===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\